subSubSection.paragraph:
Median lobe of aedeagus (
Fig. 9G
) in ventral view fusiform, with small median tooth; ventral surface with shallow median groove; in lateral view median lobe slightly and regularly curved; dorsal ligula from half length to apical part of median lobe of aedeagus, tapered toward apex. Spermatheca (
Fig. 11M
) with widely rounded basal part; collum moderately elongate, about twice as long as apical part; ductus quite short, apically inserted.
